title: iMac 820-2901-A not coming up
message:
Trigger SMC_ONOFF_L and check for pulse at P5VS3_EN.
If nothing, check for drop pulse at PM_PWRBTN_L.

title: iMac 820-2901-A not coming up
message: So PM_PWRBTN_L is stuck on 3V, no drop pulse noted?

title: iMac 820-2901-A not coming up
message:
You waste time, if don't post important information in your threads.
Don't you know yet which should be the PM_PWRBTN_L voltage?
Nothing can move on the board, if PM_RSMRST_L and PM_PWRBTN_L stay low; basic checkings...

You may have SMC problem.
Bad PCH can also pull down PM_PWRBTN_L.
